-- Finmeccanica May Sell Ansaldo Energia Stake to FSI, Sole Says
-- B y   E l i s a   M a r t i n u z z i
-- 2012-05-08T06:11:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-08/finmeccanica-may-sell-ansaldo-energia-stake-to-fsi-sole-says.html
Finmeccanica SpA (FNC)  may sell a stake in
Ansaldo Energia SpA to Fondo Strategico Italiano, a state-backed
fund, Il Sole 24 Ore reported, without saying how it obtained
the information.  Finmeccanica may sell a 40 percent stake in the unit, which
is also drawing interest from  Siemens AG (SIE) , the financial daily
reported today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Elisa Martinuzzi at 
 emartinuzzi@bloomberg.net  